                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The electronic figment's jaw stretches downward to its chest, letting out a terrible scream. All creatures within 20 feet must succeed at a @Check[will|dc:20] save or be @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2}. Creatures affected by the figment's worst nightmare ability take a –2 circumstance penalty to their save.</p>"
