                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The electronic figment can alter its appearance to resemble creatures that have previously hurt the target, whether in combat or traumatic memories. After Striking a creature, the figment's appearance changes to the creature's worst nightmare; it gains a +2 circumstance bonus to AC and saves against its target creature.</p>"
